    • isValidDate

      public boolean isValidDate(int leap)
      Check if February, SMALL, and BIG months have their correct # of days
      Parameters:
      leap -
      Returns:
      For month value of 2: true if day is smaller or equal to leap and greater than 0, false otherwise. For BIG months, true if day greater than 0 and smaller or equal to 31, false otherwise For SMALL months, true if day greater than 0 and smaller or equal to 30, false otherwise
